            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Each tool uses a proprietary algorithm and its own link index. Ahrefs weights referring domains heavily; Semrush incorporates broader authority signals including domain-level metrics. A KD 40 in Ahrefs may correspond to KD 60 in Semrush. Pick one tool and use it consistently rather than averaging across platforms.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
